Usage: set_dynamic_rail_simulation [-help] [-auto_repeat] [-reset]
                                   [-resolution <float>] [-start <float>]
                                   [-stop <float>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-auto_repeat            # repeat waveform to stop time (bool, optional)
-reset                  # reset all values (bool, optional)
-resolution <float>     # <pace in ps>
                        # (float, optional, default unit=ps, current unit = ps)
-start <float>          # <start time in ns>
                        # (float, optional, default unit=ns, current unit = ns)
-stop <float>           # <stop time in ns>
                        # (float, optional, default unit=ns, current unit = ns)